Meanwhile, the next day, the Times published a story perhaps more germane t=
o Lewis=E2=80=99s future at the Post. Central to Lewis=E2=80=99s strategy i=
s the creation of that =E2=80=9Cthird newsroom=E2=80=9D focused on =E2=80=
=9Csocial media journalism,=E2=80=9D servicing audiences on TikTok and Inst=
