If you go back further in Lewis=E2=80=99s history, there are similar questi=
ons around his attempt as editor of the Telegraph to launch a stand-alone d=
igital growth division known as =E2=80=9CProject Euston,=E2=80=9D in 2009. =
The project, another precursor to the =E2=80=9Cthird newsroom,=E2=80=9D shu=
ttered after he left the company six months later. Indeed, if there=E2=80=
=99s one revelation I=E2=80=99ve gathered from all my conversations with Po=
