6c7480d85ae70b720727f3411c80560acd514" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-decorati=
on:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">release</a></u> from a Russian pris=
on, <i>Wall Street Journal </i>reporter <b>Evan Gershkovich</b> was require=
d to write an official request for presidential clemency to <b>Vladimir Put=
in</b>. According to his paper=E2=80=99s <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.n=
ews/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dSRlJ0M2tvQTY0MVNzbHJFaUp=
aYz0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS93b3JsZC9ldXJvcGUvZXZhbi1nZXJzaG=
